<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="at-a-loss">at a loss</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>感到迷惑；不知所措：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We are at a loss as to what kind of business to start.
我们不知道该做什么生意。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Their snowy mountaintops form a beautiful picture that will leave you <strong>at a loss for words</strong> (= unable to think what to say).
它们那些白雪皑皑的山顶构成了一幅美丽的图画，美得让你无法用语言形容。</p><footer>译林② – 10</footer></div></div>